refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolmsg_send resourcequeue intmsgtype mixedmessage boolserialize boolblocking interrorcode
msg_send sends a message of type msgtype (which MUST be greater than 0) to the message queue specified by queue.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 &return.success;



 Upon successful completion the message queue data structure is updated as
 follows: msg_lspid is set to the process-ID of the
 calling process, msg_qnum is incremented by 1 and
 msg_stime is set to the current time.
